Hyperliquid changed the `WritePrecompile` to `CoreWriter` 

```
bytes memory action = abi.encodePacked(_receiver, oftAsset.coreIndexId, amounts.core);
bytes memory payload = abi.encodePacked(abi.encodePacked(SPOT_SEND_HEADER, action));
_receiverICoreWriter(HLP_PRECOMPILE_WRITE).sendRawAction(payload);
```

Also added in a `try...catch` on `sendAssetToHyperCore` and `fundAddressOnHyperCore`
